Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Ethics Transparency Module Stub
Provides comprehensive transparency and explainability capabilities for AI systems
Enables explainable AI, interpretability frameworks, and algorithmic accountability
:End Note

Type TransparencySystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    transparency_level as String
    explainability_methods as List[ExplainabilityMethod]
    interpretation_techniques as List[InterpretationTechnique]
    explanation_generators as List[ExplanationGenerator]
    transparency_protocols as List[TransparencyProtocol]
    auditability_framework as AuditabilityFramework
    documentation_system as DocumentationSystem
    system_configuration as SystemConfiguration

Type ExplainabilityMethod is Dictionary with:
    method_id as String
    method_name as String
    method_type as String
    explanation_scope as String
    method_parameters as MethodParameters
    applicability_conditions as List[ApplicabilityCondition]
    computational_complexity as ComputationalComplexity
    explanation_quality_metrics as List[QualityMetric]

Type InterpretationTechnique is Dictionary with:
    technique_id as String
    technique_name as String
    technique_type as String
    interpretation_level as String
    technique_parameters as TechniqueParameters
    output_format as OutputFormat
    interpretation_confidence as Float
    technique_limitations as List[String]

Type ExplanationGenerator is Dictionary with:
    generator_id as String
    generator_type as String
    target_audience as String
    explanation_templates as List[ExplanationTemplate]
    generation_strategy as GenerationStrategy
    personalization_capability as PersonalizationCapability
    explanation_quality_assessment as QualityAssessment

Type TransparencyProtocol is Dictionary with:
    protocol_id as String
    protocol_name as String
    protocol_scope as String
    disclosure_requirements as List[DisclosureRequirement]
    documentation_standards as List[DocumentationStandard]
    accessibility_requirements as List[AccessibilityRequirement]
    update_procedures as List[UpdateProcedure]
    compliance_verification as ComplianceVerification

Type DecisionExplanation is Dictionary with:
    explanation_id as String
    decision_context as DecisionContext
    explanation_type as String
    explanation_content as ExplanationContent
    supporting_evidence as List[SupportingEvidence]
    confidence_metrics as ConfidenceMetrics
    explanation_completeness as Float
    explanation_timestamp as Integer

Type ExplanationContent is Dictionary with:
    content_id as String
    primary_explanation as String
    detailed_explanation as String
    technical_explanation as String
    simplified_explanation as String
    visual_elements as List[VisualElement]
    mathematical_formulation as MathematicalFormulation
    example_scenarios as List[ExampleScenario]

Type ModelTransparency is Dictionary with:
    transparency_id as String
    model_architecture_disclosure as ArchitectureDisclosure
    training_data_disclosure as DataDisclosure
    parameter_disclosure as ParameterDisclosure
    decision_boundary_analysis as DecisionBoundaryAnalysis
    uncertainty_disclosure as UncertaintyDisclosure
    limitation_disclosure as LimitationDisclosure
    performance_disclosure as PerformanceDisclosure

Type AuditabilityFramework is Dictionary with:
    framework_id as String
    audit_trail_system as AuditTrailSystem
    decision_logging as DecisionLogging
    traceability_mechanisms as List[TraceabilityMechanism]
    reproducibility_protocols as List[ReproducibilityProtocol]
    verification_procedures as List[VerificationProcedure]
    audit_report_generation as AuditReportGeneration
    compliance_monitoring as ComplianceMonitoring

Type CausalExplanation is Dictionary with:
    causal_explanation_id as String
    causal_model as CausalModel
    causal_pathways as List[CausalPathway]
    counterfactual_analysis as CounterfactualAnalysis
    intervention_analysis as InterventionAnalysis
    causal_attribution as CausalAttribution
    causal_confidence as Float

Type ExplanationContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    decision_data as Dictionary
    model_context as Dictionary
    audience_requirements as Dictionary
    explanation_preferences as Dictionary
    context_metadata as Dictionary

Type DecisionContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    decision_input as Dictionary
    decision_output as Dictionary
    decision_metadata as Dictionary
    decision_timestamp as String
    context_metadata as Dictionary

Type MonitoringContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    monitoring_requirements as Dictionary
    performance_metrics as Dictionary
    effectiveness_criteria as Dictionary
    monitoring_metadata as Dictionary

Type ReportingContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    report_requirements as Dictionary
    audience_specifications as Dictionary
    format_preferences as Dictionary
    reporting_metadata as Dictionary

Process called "create_transparency_system" that takes config as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "generate_comprehensive_explanation" that takes transparency_system as Dictionary and explanation_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "generate_local_explanation" that takes transparency_system as Dictionary and decision_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "generate_global_explanation" that takes transparency_system as Dictionary and decision_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "generate_causal_explanation" that takes transparency_system as Dictionary and decision_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "generate_counterfactual_explanation" that takes transparency_system as Dictionary and decision_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_audience_specific_explanation" that takes explanation_data as Dictionary and target_audience as String and transparency_system as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "monitor_explanation_effectiveness" that takes transparency_system as Dictionary and monitoring_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_audit_trail" that takes transparency_system as Dictionary and decision_sequence as List[Dictionary] returns Dictionary
Process called "generate_transparency_report" that takes transparency_system as Dictionary and reporting_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_transparency_monitoring_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_transparency_analysis" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary 